title: Four scores for Howe as UC shuts out Harvest
text:
Four scores for Howe as UC shuts out Harvest 
Sat, Oct 3, 2015 @ 12:14 am 
UNIVERSITY CHR. 61 
HARVEST 0 
Super 11 selection Hussein Howe had three rushing TDs, returned a blocked punt for a score as UC (4-1, 1-0 in District 2-2A) hammered Harvest (0-6, 0-1). Howe rushed for 176 yards on six carries. Otis Anderson added 116 yards rushing and a pair of TDs on seven carries.
